Mollie Makes DIY Fashion - 2014  UK

132 Pages | True PDF | English | 19 MB 


Form the makers of Mollie Makes, we bring you the DIY fashion collection. This guide gives you tips and projects to making your own clothing, from vintage to Bohemian, we have something for you!  Customise your old clothes and upcycle unused garments with our easy to follow tutorials.
